            <a href="/tracker" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-white text-emerald-700 font-semibold hover:-translate-y-1 transition">Start Tracking</a>
            <a href="/tips" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-xl ring-2 ring-white font-semibold hover:bg-white/10 transition">Learn Tips</a>
